data.description: Is this a brand-new residence? No, but you might mistake it for one given the extensive interior renovations. This home boasts 3 or 4BR & 2BA, complemented by a recently refurbished pool. The comprehensive remodeling, carried out over the past months, reflects a meticulous attention to detail. Upon entry, you'll be greeted by newly sealed wood floors. The formal dining room beckons with ample space for gatherings. The kitchen, breakfast nook, and great room area are seamlessly connected and generously proportioned, featuring a 2 sided fireplace. Kitchen island & abundant counter space, coupled with recently installed and unused double ovens, cooktop, microwave, and dishwasher, elevate meal preparation to a joyous experience for even the most discerning chef. Principal suite is a haven, with space for 2 sitting areas, and a fully remodeled bathroom boasts 2 vanities, a jetted tub, and a shower. This residence invites you to preview its many details—too numerous to list comprehensively.
